563
00:59:43,906 --> 00:59:45,241
Would you stop talkin' silly?

564
00:59:45,324 --> 00:59:46,450
Get back to bed!

565
00:59:46,534 --> 00:59:49,829
- Honest, Sylvia! I wouldn't
kid about somethin' like that!

566
00:59:50,454 --> 00:59:52,957
