MY baby!

688
01:12:21,580 --> 01:12:23,206
Poor little bastard.

689
01:14:50,770 --> 01:14:52,981
Oh, Roger! I'm so glad you're here!

690
01:14:53,857 --> 01:14:54,816
That awful woman-

691
01:14:54,941 --> 01:14:56,568
- Now, you listen
